<![CDATA[<b style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font color="#cc0000" size="4">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName},</font></b><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font color="#cc0000" size="4"><br></font></b></div><div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><b><font color="#cc0000">Sales Ambassador Training at Ignite 2015&nbsp;</font></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><br></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b>Congratulations on graduating from the National Citizen Service programme and welcome to our fantastic alumni programme called The Challenge Society. Over the summer you expressed your interest in volunteering alongside our Sales Team as a Sales Ambassador in schools and colleges in your area.&nbsp;</b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><br></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><b><font color="#cc0000">Our first training event is taking place at our launch event for The Challenge Society called Ignite 2015!&nbsp;</font></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><br></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><font color="#cc0000">Where:</font> Goldsmiths University, New Cross, SE14 6NW.</b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><font color="#cc0000">When:</font> Saturday 28th of November between 11:00 and 17:00.</b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><br></b></div><div style="text-align: center; font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b><font color="#cc0000"><a href="http://tcssouthlondon.co.uk/ignite-2015/">Click here to reserve your space!&nbsp;</a></font></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><br></b></div><div style="text-align: center;"><font color="#cc0000"><b style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Featuring special guests&nbsp;</span></font></b><b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Aaron Roach Bridgeman from SBTV and a&nbsp;</span>performance<span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;by Afrikan Boy!&nbsp;</span></font></b></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></font></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">In addition to becoming an&nbsp;</span>official<span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;Sales Ambassador for The Challenge, Ignite 2015 is all about you and your future. Get involved in CV and interview workshops, personal statement sessions, money management workshops and meet a huge range of professionals!&nbsp;</span></font></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></font></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></font></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b>Really looking forward to seeing you there,&nbsp;</b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><br></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b>Rhiannon&nbsp;</b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b>Graduate Associate Manager - South East London</b></div></div>]]></td>
